Rating: 2
This dish was pretty good, but let's not get carried away -- it's not a 4-forker. I would probably give it 2.5 if I could, but I can't, so I won't. :( The marinade is serviceable, but it's far from inspired. Ditto for the veggies. Sure, everyone likes cherry tomatoes with their swordfish, but this is nothing unusual, and there are no surprises. Okay in a pinch -- or if you're feeling just plain lazy.

